{"tid":603643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【講夠未】劉鶴與美財政部長通話 指美國違背國際貿易規則","createTime":"2018-03-24T02:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T02:50:13.000Z","uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"543269cf96e905203f4744bffccf35aee5cd88ab","tid":603643,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"新華社北京3月24日電3月24日上午，中央政治局委員、國務院副總理、中財辦主任、中美全面經濟對話中方牽頭人劉鶴應約與美國財政部長姆努欽通話。姆努欽向中方通報了美方公布301調查報告最新情況。劉鶴表示，美方近日公布301調查報告，違背國際貿易規則，不利於中方利益，不利於美方利益，不利於全球利益。中方已經做好準備，有實力捍衛國家利益，希望雙方保持理性，共同努力，維護中美經貿關系總體穩定的大局。雙方同意繼續就此保持溝通。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.163.com/18/0324/10/DDLHAPDF00018AOQ.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.163.com%2F18%2F0324%2F10%2FDDLHAPDF00018AOQ.html&d=2aAya40zwwW3sWBkcJntq5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=88f8ceed\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.163.com/18/0324/10/DDLHAPDF00018AOQ.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newstatesman.com/sites/default/files/styles/nodeimage/public/blogs_2017/09/gettyimages-634136694.jpg?itok=hbx6DFpn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newstatesman.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fnodeimage%2Fpublic%2Fblogs_2017%2F09%2Fgettyimages-634136694.jpg%3Fitok%3Dhbx6DFpn&h=79fe63cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61e0ccd407c5c3aabefefec5da7ea1e13660d0f0","tid":603643,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"WTO"}]}